</P>
<P>
Washington, D.C. 20013 
</P>
<P>
(800) 842-2200 
</P>
<P>
Bank Melli Iran 
</P>
<P>
Iran Quake Relief Assistance 
</P>
<P>
Account No. 5000 
</P>
<P>
628 Madison Ave. 
</P>
<P>
New York, N.Y. 10022 
</P>
<P>
U.S. Committee for UNICEF 
</P>
<P>
333 E. 38th St. 
</P>
<P>
New York, N.Y. 10016 
</P>
<P>
(212) 686-5522 
</P>
