Boulevard. CARLOS CHAVEZ / Los Angeles TimesFOR RO PIX SLUGGED AMNESTY; Photo, 
Neena Zafar and son, Wajahat, 5 months, were at the Valley office at 5 a.m. 
Friday but were not allowed in. Zafar said she would return. CARLOS CHAVEZ / 
Los Angeles Times 
</P>
