<TEXT>
<P>
Are my ears deceiving me or did I hear Baker imply that the new Israeli 
government might be something less than sincere in its claim to be longing for 
peace! From a Palestinian's perspective nothing is being done any more 
ruthlessly with the advent of this new government than has been done almost 
every day for the last 40 years! The Palestinians have been chased off their 
land, beaten, detained, tortured, deprived of their human rights, their civil 
liberties. 
</P>
