TERRORISM -- ISRAEL; PALESTINE LIBERATION FRONT; ISRAEL -- REVOLTS; MEETINGS; 
UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- EGYPT; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS 
-- ISRAEL 
</P>
