<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEWSWIRE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Members of the NCAA Infractions Committee will hear Nevada Las Vegas' final 
presentation today in the NCAA's case against basketball Coach Jerry Tarkanian. 
</P>
<P>
A decision is not expected for about two weeks. 
</P>
<P>
Tarkanian, who led the Rebels to an NCAA title this year, is not expected to be 
formally suspended for violations stemming from a case 13 years ago. 
</P>
